28:25.210 --> 28:28.000
- Wow, accident,
you both make out!

28:28.000 --> 28:29.170
What, you both plan
this little witness

28:29.170 --> 28:30.220
for the prosecution stunt?

28:30.220 --> 28:32.170
- Objection.
JUDGE: Sustained!

28:32.170 --> 28:34.200
- You both conspire to kill her,
setting him up as our witness?

28:34.200 --> 28:37.000
- Objection!
