28:47.110 --> 28:50.000
He plugged his equipment
into your outlet.

28:50.000 --> 28:51.220
There's some case law,
theft of electricity.

28:51.220 --> 28:54.000
- That feels like a stretch.
- It'll buy us a warrant.

28:54.000 --> 28:55.220
Get Eugene.

28:57.040 --> 28:59.210
- Mr. Lawrence Conley?
- Yeah.

28:59.210 --> 29:02.040
- You're under arrest.
- For what?

29:02.040 --> 29:04.210
- Theft of electricity
and trespass.

29:04.210 --> 29:06.090
- What?
- We have a search warrant.

29:06.090 --> 29:07.210
- Wait--what the hell
