29:07.210 --> 29:09.110
- Read him his rights.

29:09.110 --> 29:11.000
- What are you looking for,
stolen electricity?

29:11.000 --> 29:12.090
OFFICER: You have the right
to remain silent.

29:12.090 --> 29:14.020
- Bobby.

29:14.020 --> 29:15.120
OFFICER: Anything you say
can and will be used

29:15.120 --> 29:16.220
against you in a court of law.

29:16.220 --> 29:18.180
You have the right
to seek an attorney,

29:18.180 --> 29:20.230
and have an attorney present
during questioning.

29:20.230 --> 29:22.230
If you so desire--

29:22.230 --> 29:24.190
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

29:24.190 --> 29:26.050
- Uh, do me a favor Mac.

29:26.050 --> 29:28.120
