don't hurt him.

29:45.130 --> 29:47.020
- She's a teenager
and a friend of mine,

29:47.020 --> 29:49.170
you sick bastard.
DETECTIVE MCGUIRE: Okay, Bobby.

29:49.170 --> 29:52.060
I said, okay, Bobby.

29:52.060 --> 29:54.200
- [gasping]

29:54.200 --> 29:56.090
They were security tapes.

29:56.090 --> 29:59.070
- [grunts]

30:00.210 --> 30:02.070
- We'll take it from here.
- [panting]

30:04.020 --> 30:12.000
<i>♪</i> ♪

30:13.200 --> 30:15.130
- Basically,
