40:33.150 --> 40:36.060
- [chuckles]

40:36.060 --> 40:37.130
- Thank you.

40:37.130 --> 40:39.100
- For what?

40:39.100 --> 40:42.150
- For being there.

40:42.150 --> 40:44.170
It helped.

40:44.170 --> 40:47.070
- Well, whatever I could do.

40:59.080 --> 41:02.070
- Will the defendant
please, rise?

41:05.020 --> 41:07.090
Mr. Foreman,
has the jury reached a verdict?

41:07.090 --> 41:09.150
- We have, Your Honor.
- What say you?

41:09.150 --> 41:11.160
- Commonwealth versus
Gordon Armbrust,

41:11.160 --> 41:14.080
on the count of murder
in the second-degree,

41:14.080 --> 41:17.110
we find the defendant,
Gordon Armbrust,

41:17.110 --> 41:19.030
not guilty.

41:19.030 --> 41:22.020
[murmuring]

41:23.110 --> 41:25.070
JUDGE:
The defendant is free to go.

41:25.070 --> 41:27.100
Jury is dismissed
with the thanks of the court.

41:27.100 --> 41:29.180
