[gavel bangs]

41:33.120 --> 41:36.120
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

41:36.120 --> 41:39.080
<i>♪</i> ♪

41:39.080 --> 41:41.080
- Congratulations.

41:41.080 --> 41:45.130
<i>♪</i> ♪

41:45.130 --> 41:46.220
- Gary Armbrust,

41:46.220 --> 41:48.010
