42:16.150 --> 42:18.140
- Is this true?

42:18.140 --> 42:21.000
Can I get life?

42:21.000 --> 42:22.200
Tell me!

42:22.200 --> 42:24.050
- Don't say anything to anybody.

42:24.050 --> 42:25.170
I'll be right back
to talk to you.

42:25.170 --> 42:27.160
- What the hell is going on?

42:28.210 --> 42:33.180
